## Roadmap

- [ ] Import existing OPML files
- [ ] Export feeds as OPML file
- [ ] Set article as unread
- [ ] Set a feed as read
- [ ] Set an article as favorite
- [ ] Tags system for articles
- [ ] Add notes on articles
- [ ] Feeds auto-sync
- [ ] Edit existing feeds
- [ ] Search articles by name/content
 
